1. [discipline:default] [reference/exec-pause-verb]
   Atomic rename .gm/prd.yml → .gm/prd.paused.yml; question text from body becomes header comment. Returns permission deny to halt tool call. prompt_submit.rs auto-renames back at next user turn. Added 2026-04-25 rs-plugkit commit 13fa81d.
